OL,6,FDefault are helping cut speeds and
OL,7,Fwill save lives, the Welsh government
OL,8,Fhas insisted.
OL,10,FData collected by Transport for Wales
OL,11,F(TfW) shows that drivers are
OL,12,Ftravelling on average 4mph slower on
OL,13,Fmain roads in Wales since the rollout
OL,14,Fof a new lower speed limit for built-
OL,15,Fup areas.
OL,17,FThe Welsh Labour government, , insists
OL,18,Fthe lower speeds will lead to fewer
OL,19,Fcollisions and people injured.
