OL,3,CMotorists driving 4mph slower on
OL,4,Caverage since default 20mph roll out
OL,6,FBut the change has seen fierce
OL,7,Fopposition from the Conservatives in
OL,8,Fthe Senedd, who have branded it a
OL,9,F"waste of time and resources".
OL,11,FThe TfW data shows that average speeds
OL,12,Fhave dropped from 28.9mph to 24.8mph
OL,13,Fsince the measure was put in place.
OL,15,FResearch undertaken by the Transport
OL,16,FResearch Laboratory, a transport
OL,17,Fconsultancy, in 2000 suggested there
OL,18,Fis an average 6% reduction in
OL,19,Fcollisions with each 1mph reduction in
OL,20,Faverage speed on urban roads.
