OL,6,FLee Waters MS, the deputy minister for
OL,7,Fclimate change, said: "The latest data
OL,8,Fpublished today is clear evidence that
OL,9,Faverage speeds are coming down on
OL,10,Froads across Wales.
OL,12,F"We also know from data published by
OL,13,FGo Safe earlier this month that 97% of
OL,14,Fdrivers are complying with the new
OL,15,Fslower speed limit ` behaviours and
OL,16,Fattitudes towards 20mph are beginning
OL,17,Fto change.
