OL,6,F"We've still got a way to go, but it's
OL,7,Fencouraging to see that things are
OL,8,Fmoving in the right direction. Every
OL,9,F1mph reduction in speed makes a real
OL,10,Fdifference ` so this is a real turning
OL,11,Fpoint."
OL,13,FMr Waters added that evidence was
OL,14,Fclear that lower speeds would help
OL,15,Fsave lives, lead to fewer injuries and
OL,16,Freduce the impact on the NHS.
