OL,6,FRoss Moorlock, chief executive of the
OL,7,Froad charity Brake, said the reduced
OL,8,Fspeed was "encouraging" and called on
OL,9,Fthe UK government to follow Wales'
OL,10,Flead.
OL,12,FHe said: "Every day, five people die
OL,13,Fon UK roads and speed is a factor in
OL,14,Fevery crash. The faster we drive, the
OL,15,Fgreater our risk of crashing, and the
OL,16,Fharder we hit if we do crash.
OL,18,F"We know that road crashes have a
OL,19,Fdevastating impact on families and
OL,20,Fcommunities."
